[section#depr.impldec
    [:en] Implicit declaration of copy functions
    [:zh_CN] 复制函数的隐式声明
]

[para]
[:en] The implicit definition of a copy constructor as defaulted is deprecated
if the class has a user-declared copy assignment operator or a user-declared
destructor.
[:zh_CN] 当类具有用户声明的复制赋值运算符或者用户声明的析构函数，则将复制构造
函数隐式定义为预置是被摒弃的。

[:en] The implicit definition of a copy assignment operator as defaulted is
deprecated if the class has a user-declared copy constructor or a user-declared
destructor ([#class.dtor], [#class.copy]).
[:zh_CN] 当类具有用户声明的复制构造函数或者用户声明的析构函数，则将复制赋值
运算符隐式定义为预置是被摒弃的（[#class.dtor]，[#class.copy]）。

[:en] In a future revision of this International Standard, these implicit
definitions could become deleted ([#dcl.fct.def]).
[:zh_CN] 本国际标准的某个未来版本中，这些隐式定义将会变为弃置的
（[#dcl.fct.def]）。
